Type: Package
Package: Shearwater
Title: Analyze Wedge-Tailed Shearwater Movement and Fisheries Overlap
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Cooper", "Owen", email = "coopernowen@berkeley.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for cleaning GPS tracking data, segmenting trips,
    calculating movement metrics, and analyzing fisheries overlap for
    wedge-tailed shearwaters.
